rows.label: tlk70000056_03_msg0001
rows.name:
Some adults can be scary, but all the
people here are really nice to me.

rows.label: tlk70000056_03_msg0002
rows.name:
Lotsa people knew about my da,
so they felt sorry for me and fussed.
Nice of them to do it, really.

rows.label: tlk70000056_03_msg0003
rows.name:
No need to feel sorry for me now
though! After all, I get to be with Kei
and my da, so I'm real happy.

rows.label: tlk70000056_03_msg0004
rows.name:
Some things make you feel sorry for
someone, but mostly, life is just hard.
You don't need special pity for that!
